  <div class="container px-5">
    <div class="row gx-5 justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-xl-8">
        <div class="h2 fs-1 text-white mb-4">"I hired Macron to motivate my students, it worked really well! All my students are now investment bankers."</div>
        <img src="assets/lewagon-logo.webp" alt="le-wagon-logo" style="height: 3rem" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>
